label: Curve
comment: A multi-purpose curve or functional relationship between an independent variable (X-axis) and dependent (Y-axis) variables.

label: SignalConfiguration
comment: A configuration or a set of signals selected for recording during a simulation.

label: SignalRecorder
comment: A recorder for a given signal.

label: SimulationEvents
comment: A configuration or a set of events executed during a simulation.

label: SimulationResultCharacteristic
comment: Result characteristic. The xvalue of the curve is time.

label: SimulationSettings
comment: Describes simulation settings necessary for a simulation.
